<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
		<title>Ripple Union Interac e-Transfers</title>
		<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/assets/common.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<h1><a href="//rippleunion.com"><img src="/assets/logo.png" alt="Ripple Union" /></a> Interac e-Transfers</h1>

		<section>
			<h1>Transfer to IOUs</h1>
			<p>This form allows you to send us an Interac e-Transfer, after which we will send CAD IOUs to your Ripple address, less a 2 CAD fee.  If necessary, your account will be activated with 35 XRP* and you will receive an email from our staff with further instructions.</p>

			<p>This service is limited to {{serviceLimit}} CAD per user per day.</p>

			<p>An automated service will verify your telephone number shortly after you submit this form.  In some cases, our staff may also call you to further verify your identity and may ask for your birth date and/or mailing address.</p>

			<p>Please allow up to 2 business days for processing.</p>

			<p>Telephone number must be a full 10-digit North American number.</p>

			<p>* Please note that the activation amount is subject to change based on the Ripple network's activation limits.</p>

			<form method="post" action="{{depositFormAction}}">
				{{{renderedDepositForm}}}
				<button type="submit">Send</button>
			</form>
		</section>
	</body>
</html>
